{"title":"To A Sad Daughter","author":{"name":"Michael Ondaatje"},"publishDate":"2012-01-18","lines":[{"line":"All night long the hockey pictures","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"gaze down at you","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"sleeping in your tracksuit.","stanza":1,"number":3},{"line":"Belligerent goalies are your ideal.","stanza":1,"number":4},{"line":"Threats of being traded","stanza":1,"number":5},{"line":"cuts and wounds","stanza":1,"number":6},{"line":"–all this pleases you.","stanza":1,"number":7},{"line":"O my god! you say at breakfast","stanza":1,"number":8},{"line":"reading the sports page over the Alpen","stanza":1,"number":9},{"line":"as another player breaks his ankle","stanza":1,"number":10},{"line":"or assaults the coach.","stanza":1,"number":11},{"line":"When I thought of daughters","stanza":2,"number":12},{"line":"I wasn’t expecting this","stanza":2,"number":13},{"line":"but I like this more.","stanza":2,"number":14},{"line":"I like all your faults","stanza":2,"number":15},{"line":"even your purple moods","stanza":2,"number":16},{"line":"when you retreat from everyone","stanza":2,"number":17},{"line":"to sit in bed under a quilt.","stanza":2,"number":18},{"line":"And when I say ‘like’","stanza":2,"number":19},{"line":"I mean of course ‘love’","stanza":2,"number":20},{"line":"but that embarrasses you.","stanza":2,"number":21},{"line":"You who feel superior to black and white movies","stanza":2,"number":22},{"line":"(coaxed for hours to see Casablanca)","stanza":2,"number":23},{"line":"though you were moved","stanza":2,"number":24},{"line":"by Creature from the Black Lagoon.","stanza":2,"number":25},{"line":"One day I’ll come swimming","stanza":3,"number":26},{"line":"beside your ship or someone will","stanza":3,"number":27},{"line":"and if you hear the siren","stanza":3,"number":28},{"line":"listen to it. For if you close your ears","stanza":3,"number":29},{"line":"only nothing happens. You will never change.","stanza":3,"number":30},{"line":"I don’t care if you risk","stanza":4,"number":31},{"line":"your life to angry goalies","stanza":4,"number":32},{"line":"creatures with webbed feet.","stanza":4,"number":33},{"line":"You can enter their caves and castles","stanza":4,"number":34},{"line":"their glass laboratories. Just","stanza":4,"number":35},{"line":"don’t be fooled by anyone but yourself.","stanza":4,"number":36},{"line":"This is the first lecture I’ve given you.","stanza":5,"number":37},{"line":"You’re ‘sweet sixteen’ you said.","stanza":5,"number":38},{"line":"I’d rather be your closest friend","stanza":5,"number":39},{"line":"than your father. I’m not good at advice","stanza":5,"number":40},{"line":"you know that, but ride","stanza":5,"number":41},{"line":"the ceremonies","stanza":5,"number":42},{"line":"until they grow dark.","stanza":5,"number":43},{"line":"Sometimes you are so busy","stanza":6,"number":44},{"line":"discovering your friends","stanza":6,"number":45},{"line":"I ache with loss","stanza":6,"number":46},{"line":"–but that is greed.","stanza":6,"number":47},{"line":"And sometimes I’ve gone","stanza":6,"number":48},{"line":"into my purple world","stanza":6,"number":49},{"line":"and lost you.","stanza":6,"number":50},{"line":"One afternoon I stepped","stanza":7,"number":51},{"line":"into your room. You were sitting","stanza":7,"number":52},{"line":"at the desk where I now write this.","stanza":7,"number":53},{"line":"Forsythia outside the window","stanza":7,"number":54},{"line":"and sun spilled over you","stanza":7,"number":55},{"line":"like a thick yellow miracle","stanza":7,"number":56},{"line":"as if another planet","stanza":7,"number":57},{"line":"was coaxing you out of the house","stanza":7,"number":58},{"line":"–all those possible worlds!–","stanza":7,"number":59},{"line":"and you, meanwhile, busy with mathematics.","stanza":7,"number":60},{"line":"I cannot look at forsythia now","stanza":8,"number":61},{"line":"without loss, or joy for you.","stanza":8,"number":62},{"line":"You step delicately","stanza":8,"number":63},{"line":"into the wild world","stanza":8,"number":64},{"line":"and your real prize will be","stanza":8,"number":65},{"line":"the frantic search.","stanza":8,"number":66},{"line":"Want everything. If you break","stanza":8,"number":67},{"line":"break going out not in.","stanza":8,"number":68},{"line":"How you live your life I don’t care","stanza":8,"number":69},{"line":"but I’ll sell my arms for you,","stanza":8,"number":70},{"line":"hold your secrets forever.","stanza":8,"number":71},{"line":"If I speak of death","stanza":9,"number":72},{"line":"which you fear now, greatly,","stanza":9,"number":73},{"line":"it is without answers.","stanza":9,"number":74},{"line":"Except that each","stanza":9,"number":75},{"line":"one we know is","stanza":9,"number":76},{"line":"in our blood.","stanza":9,"number":77},{"line":"Don’t recall graves.","stanza":9,"number":78},{"line":"Memory is permanent.","stanza":9,"number":79},{"line":"Remember the afternoon’s","stanza":9,"number":80},{"line":"yellow suburban annunciation.","stanza":9,"number":81},{"line":"Your goalie","stanza":9,"number":82},{"line":"in his frightening mask","stanza":9,"number":83},{"line":"dreams perhaps","stanza":9,"number":84},{"line":"of gentleness.","stanza":9,"number":85}]}